*Advokata* je učestvovao u nizu složenih parnica. (The lawyer has participated in a number of complex lawsuits.)

*Advokatu* su ponuđene brojne privilegije. (The lawyer was offered numerous privileges.)

Sud je uvažio predlog *advokata*. (The court took into consideration the lawyer's proposal.)

Sudija je ukazao *advokati* da se pridržava propisa. (The judge admonished the lawyer to comply with the regulations.)

*Advokatima* je uskraćeno pravo da se pojave pred sudom. (The lawyers were denied the right to appear in court.)